      Are birds pet animals?
      Before buying or adopting a pet bird, make sure a bird is the right type of pet for your family. Know that many pet birds have a very long life span. Some parrots can live for 20 years or longer. Birds require special care and can sometimes carry germs that can make people sick.

      How is a pet bird?
      A pet bird is friendly, gentle, and well-suited to being a companion. These traits are important for people with limited pet bird experience. It's easier to bond with and care for an animal that has a naturally friendly disposition, rather than one that tends to be timid or aggressive.Sep 26, 2022
